properties.name: Color
properties.expression: thisLayer.effect('Colored Stroke')('Lower Rounding') > 0 ? thisLayer.effect('Colored Stroke')('Middle Color') : thisLayer.effect('Colored Stroke')('End Color')

properties.name: Position
properties.expression: thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Base Path Lower').content('Lower Path').path.pointOnPath(thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Middle Color Lower').content('Trim Paths 1').end * 0.01)

properties.name: Scale
properties.expression: [thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Middle Color Lower').content('Stroke 1').strokeWidth, thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Middle Color Lower').content('Stroke 1').strokeWidth * thisLayer.effect('Colored Stroke')('Lower Rounding') * 0.01]

properties.name: Rotation
properties.expression: const myTrim = thisLayer.clamp(thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Middle Color Lower').content('Trim Paths 1').end * 0.01, 0.0001, 0.999)thisLayer.radiansToDegrees(Math.atan2(thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Base Path Lower').content('Lower Path').path.normalOnPath(myTrim)[1], thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Base Path Lower').content('Lower Path').path.normalOnPath(myTrim)[0]))

properties.name: Color
properties.expression: thisLayer.effect('Colored Stroke')('Upper Rounding') > 0 ? thisLayer.effect('Colored Stroke')('Start Color') : thisLayer.effect('Colored Stroke')('Middle Color')

properties.name: Scale
properties.expression: [thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Upper Color').content('Stroke 1').strokeWidth, thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Upper Color').content('Stroke 1').strokeWidth * thisLayer.effect('Colored Stroke')('Upper Rounding') * 0.01]

properties.name: Rotation
properties.expression: const myTrim = thisLayer.clamp(thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Upper Color').content('Trim Paths 1').end* 0.01, 0.0001, 0.999)thisLayer.radiansToDegrees(Math.atan2(thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Base Path Upper').content('Upper Path').path.normalOnPath(myTrim)[1], thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Base Path Upper').content('Upper Path').path.normalOnPath(myTrim)[0]))

properties.name: Stroke Width
properties.expression: const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');const scaleFactor = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('scaleFactor').transform.scale[0];const widthScale = endctrl.effect('Limber')('Width Scale') * 0.01;thisLayer.effect('Colored Stroke')('Stroke Width') * scaleFactor * widthScale;

properties.name: Path
properties.expression: function upperStrokePath() {        const thisProp = thisProperty;        const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');        const curveLin = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('curvature').transform.scale[1] * 0.01;        if (curveLin === 0) {            return thisProp.createPath([                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p1').transform.position.value,                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p2ikfkfreek').transform.position.value,            ], [], [], false);        }        else {            const inTangPos = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('curvature').transform.anchorPoint.value;            const outTangPos = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('curvature').transform.position.value;            return thisProp.createPath([                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p1').transform.position.value,                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p2ikfkfreek').transform.position.value,            ], [[0, 0], inTangPos], [[0, 0], thisLayer.mul(outTangPos, -1)], false);        }    }upperStrokePath();

properties.name: Stroke Width
properties.expression: const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');const scaleFactor = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('scaleFactor').transform.scale[0];const widthScale = endctrl.effect('Limber')('Width Scale') * 0.01;thisLayer.effect('Colored Stroke')('Stroke Width') * scaleFactor * widthScale;
